data.text:
What are your favorite brands?

The Infatuation, Headspace, Equinox, Hoxton Hotels, Pacifico, and Costco

What do you like to do outside of work for fun?

Cook, Travel/Adventure, Beach, Read, Stay Active

If you could teach a class on any topic, what would it be?

Creating and organizing space to function efficiently

What’s the best piece of advice you’ve ever been given?

Never Give Up!

If you could join any fictional family, which would it be?

The Taylors (Friday Night Lights)

What is the best thing you’ve bought this year?

Breville Barista Espresso Machine
